{
  "stem": "5470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But let me finish this first, because otherwise I'm losing my [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] thread here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- so I was completely idle, couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that's where I'm a bit out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What was I going to say here?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Can you stop it here a second?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was completely idle there now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the build up of the underground movement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to try to keep me in some sort of the other way there in the camp itself now, because they knew already that the intentions were to bring quite a number of Jewish people into the camp and transport them from there on to Germany, that there was a need for a food distribution office.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the coupons, the people who were coming in hardly had any with them than their own luggage, and the coupons weren't there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they couldn't buy the stuff needed for their-- their living.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there, the contact came with another department.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the Economic Department, under which the distribution was formed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, well, the best thing we can do is form an office under direct control of The Hague, where the head office was, and appoint someone there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where they found me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, well, he has got already the experience in the food distribution.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why not him?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was at the time at the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was I, 23?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then a leader could not be appointed before the age of 25.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I got one who was appointed over me, and he was a bad fellow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was really nasty.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
